; Test commodity compare: different semantic flags
; Fixated vs non-fixated lot prices have different flags
2024/01/01 Buy A
    Assets:Stocks    10 AAPL {$100.00}
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Buy B
    Assets:Stocks    10 AAPL {=$100.00}
    Assets:Cash

test bal Assets:Stocks --lot-prices --lots
      10 AAPL {$100}
     10 AAPL {=$100}  Assets:Stocks
end test
